WEBVTT

00:01.300 --> 00:04.975
<i>I attended Mr. Delaney's
funeral and a ghost appeared,</i>

00:05.100 --> 00:07.775
<i>a son we all thought
dead in Africa.</i>

00:07.900 --> 00:09.425
James Keziah Delaney.

00:09.550 --> 00:11.775
Dear Lord Almighty,
is that your brother?

00:11.900 --> 00:13.725
Your father was poisoned.

00:13.850 --> 00:16.450
I would say heavy doses
over a short period.

00:16.575 --> 00:20.725
One thing Africa did not cure is
that I still love you.

00:20.850 --> 00:21.925
<i>Now he is returned</i>

00:22.050 --> 00:25.425
<i>and Delaney's will leaves him
everything, including Nootka.</i>

00:25.550 --> 00:28.975
Britain and the United States
are currently at war.

00:29.100 --> 00:31.775
Sell this land
for a reasonable price.

00:31.900 --> 00:33.575
Nootka Sound is not for sale.

00:33.700 --> 00:36.775
I can give you whatever you like...
boys, girls.

00:36.900 --> 00:38.300
You have two hours to get out.

00:38.425 --> 00:41.025
I know things about the dead.

00:41.150 --> 00:43.775
I'd hoped to settle this matter
in a modern way,

00:43.900 --> 00:46.850
but that is not going to be
possible. He's all yours.

00:46.975 --> 00:48.925
This Nootka Sound is a curse.

00:49.050 --> 00:51.700
It will bring the King and Empire
down upon your head.

